	<article class="post-625569 post type-post status-publish hentry category-financial-services category-hedge-funds category-restructuringbankruptcy tag-argentina tag-elliott-management-corp tag-government-bonds tag-griesa-thomas-p tag-hedge-funds tag-kirchner-cristina-fernandez-de tag-suits-and-litigation-civil per-griesa-thomas-p per-kirchner-cristina-fernandez-de des-government-bonds des-hedge-funds des-suits-and-litigation-civil org-elliott-management-corp geo-argentina news_keywords-argentina news_keywords-cristina-fernandez-de-kirchner news_keywords-elliott-management news_keywords-government-bond news_keywords-hedge-fund-2 news_keywords-lawsuits news_keywords-thomas-griesa" id="post-625569">
